Execute Push Promotions Faster

Configure system settings to change how batch processes are orchestrated. As a result, the Push Promotions process completed faster.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise and Unlimited editions where Consumer Goods Cloud Trade Promotion Management is enabled.

How: Go to Custom Settings in Setup and add a system setting with Orchestrator as the value.
title: Configure Push Promotions Faster in Salesforce
